<br>
If you're buffed above 3k, casting Lifeburn will be auto aggro to whatever your fighting on a raid. (it will drop you to below 10 percent) <br>
<br>
I either keep Quivering Veil of Xarn memmed and spam cast it immediatly after casting Lifeburn, or Death Peace, same thing.<br>
<br>
However, the safest route is to get a rune cast on you before casting LifeBurn, so when the mob attacks you, you have time to get Death Peace or Quivering cast.<br>
<br>
